						<td>3 Gold Pieces</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td><a href="http://domulti:3">Keg of beer</a></td>
						<td>4 Gold Pieces</td>
						<td></td>
						<td></td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</p>
			<p>
				Other items these simple shops supply are hardly useful to you -- thick furs, evil-looking animal traps, harpoons and the like.
